data.description: You'll fall in love with this very clean well-maintained home just minutes from everything in Hot Springs!  New windows, granite countertops, and a great updated master suite are just a few of the features that you'll find to be must haves. The covered carport seating area is a great place to sit outside and relax or grill out on the beautiful back deck.
